    public class AddDoNotCacheConditionToAssertions
extends AbstractConditionalProfileAction
    Action to add a DoNotCacheCondition to every Assertion in a Response message. If the containing Conditions is not present, it will be created.
    Event:
    EventIds.PROCEED_EVENT_ID, EventIds.INVALID_MSG_CTX
